data.description: Price Improvement!! Location Location Location!!  Designated for North Point School Zone. Build that Garage ,Carport or add an addition on  this  property! Vision is Limitless! Vacant and Move in ready just in time for the holidays. Near Military  sites.  This Beautiful 5-Bedroom 2.5 Bath home is located in a nice neighborhood which is convenient to shopping and restaurants in both Charles County and PG County. Resting in the peaceful community of Fox Run, this idyllic and stylish home located in a Cul -DE -Sec is the best of the best! With  a spacious fully fenced Flat back yard with retainer wall and an attached deck. This home epitomizes R&R and offers unbeatable entertainment space! Newer Waterless water tank.  roof that is 13 years young! All new bathrooms, to include new vanities,  Generous sized bedrooms. Owners' suite with private bath. Move in ready and waiting for you!  Awesome brick fireplace just in time for the cooler nights Enjoy the slower pace with countless activities and amenities nearby while occasionally indulging in all the excitement that city life has to offer. In less than 30 minutes, you could be eating oysters on the half shell in National Harbor. Andrews AFB, Downtown DC, Ronald Reagan International and Old Town Alexandria are all less than 40 minutes away! Beaches and island hideaways can be reached in under an hour. A better location cannot be found! Home Warranty.  Must view immediately!
